com.interpss.dstab.device

Interface DynamicBusDevice

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, DynamicDevice, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IDynamicSimulation, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DynLoadModel, InductionMotor, LD1PAC, ScriptDynamicBusDevice
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DynamicBusDeviceImpl, DynLoadModelImpl, InductionMotorImpl, LD1PACImpl, ScriptDynamicBusDeviceImpl

    public interface DynamicBusDevice
extends DynamicDevice
    A representation of the model object 'Dynamic Bus Device'. Class for defining dynamic bus device

    The following features are supported:

    • Device Type
    • DStab Bus
    See Also:
    DstabDevicePackage.getDynamicBusDevice()
